{"title":"Combined feed","url":"https://Vinnl.github.io/feeds/all.xml","elements":[{"title":"The Luck of Cumberland (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <i><b><a href=\"/wiki/The_Luck_of_Cumberland\" title=\"The Luck of Cumberland\">The Luck of Cumberland</a></b></i> <i>(pictured)</i>, designed by <a href=\"/wiki/Herbert_Maryon\" title=\"Herbert Maryon\">Herbert Maryon</a> and executed by the <a href=\"/wiki/Keswick_School_of_Industrial_Art\" title=\"Keswick School of Industrial Art\">Keswick School of Industrial Art</a>, is made of more than 200 ounces of solid silver?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Luck_of_Cumberland","retrieved":1777705921277},{"title":"Roy Waldo Miner (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <b><a href=\"/wiki/Roy_Waldo_Miner\" title=\"Roy Waldo Miner\">Roy Waldo Miner</a></b> extracted about forty tons of coral from the <a href=\"/wiki/Andros,_The_Bahamas\" title=\"Andros, The Bahamas\">Andros Barrier Reef</a> to build a museum diorama?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Roy_Waldo_Miner","retrieved":1777705921278},{"title":"Waahine Toa (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that the <i><b><a href=\"/wiki/Waahine_Toa\" title=\"Waahine Toa\">Waahine Toa</a></b></i> paintings were criticised as unfashionable when first exhibited in the 1980s, but are now considered iconic in New Zealand art?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Waahine_Toa","retrieved":1777705921279},{"title":"Valentin Senn (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that NFL player <b><a href=\"/wiki/Valentin_Senn\" title=\"Valentin Senn\">Valentin Senn</a></b> used to play the trumpet in the Swarovski Orchestra?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Valentin_Senn","retrieved":1777705921280},{"title":"an autobiographical novel (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <a href=\"/wiki/B._S._Johnson\" title=\"B. S. Johnson\">B.&nbsp;S. Johnson</a> based <b><a href=\"/wiki/Trawl\" title=\"Trawl\">an autobiographical novel</a></